  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Planibel Hotel &amp; Apartment complex is a popular choice for British skiers and its convenience and flexible accommodation make it ideal for families and groups. It has a superb location at the bottom of the main slopes and next to the ski lifts. Facilities include spacious lounges, bar, restaurant, large wellness centre free to the hotel guests, non-ski kindergarten for 4-11 years from 20 Dec - 1 Apr, 9.30am-12.30pm &amp; 2-6pm, excl. lunch and payable direct in the resort. Hotel rooms have bath or shower, wc, balcony, satellite TV, telephone, hairdryer and minibar.</p>]]></description>
